item.title: Giant Bombcast 789: Ewoks and Hobbits
item.description: Our dear friend Lucy James is here with us and with the Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom finally here we ask the question that's on all our minds: Do you think Ewoks are better than Hobbits? Feed: https://www.giantbomb.com/podcast-xml/giant-bombcast

item.title: Streaming payouts, Ed vs Ed, Who’s DIDE?
item.description: Streaming simply doesn’t pay the bills! The discussion about streaming payouts has been going on for years. And now Snoop Dogg joined the debate: “That sh*t don’t add up!” Kikelomo speaks to Darren Hemmings of Motive Unknown about what needs to change and about what we as fans can do to support our favorite artists... Feed: https://electronicbeats.podigee.io/feed/mp3
